Dialogue Text: Oh this is indeed the place I remembered!
Thank goodness, it seems like my compass is finally working again.
In the past, this compass would always guide a certain friend of mine to Delphia.
She really liked that friend so much, she'd label him the "special guest" of hers haha!
...Who was that friend again...? Maybe Delphia might have a better idea... Anyway, here, take this. May it guide you on your journey.
